Since I was sworn in to the U.S. Senate, I’ve worked tirelessly to defend Georgia families, farmers, #smallbiz, front-line workers, law enforcement and everyone in between.
 
Through COVID-19 & beyond, the well-being of Georgians will continue to be my number one priority. https://t.co/1fDSIsJAAg
